{"tid":2446751,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解補習中介可以呃食咁多年？","createTime":"2021-03-14T16:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T05:07:35.000Z","uid":296936,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b142f4cca1b378314e5a091247d4f8bf381c0f8b","tid":2446751,"uid":296936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T16:39:36.000Z","msg":"話說最近係深水埗見到張街招<br />\n<br />\n諗住搵下外快<br />\n<br />\n點知原來又係呃人既<br />\n<br />\n大家真係要小心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FRjpWbP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFRjpWbP.jpg&h=c52f9bea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我就send 左d 水晶諗住叫佢幫我散下貨la<br />\n<br />\n佢就send 左兩張圖比我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvt6p6o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpvt6p6o.jpg&h=e0fa11c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w8awBc4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw8awBc4.jpg&h=1daec373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後佢就聊我去私補<br />\n<br />\n但越講越奇怪<br />\n<br />\n一google 原來條友叫文寶強<br />\n<br />\n有晒前科<br />\n<br />\n打佢個電話號碼會係junkcall見到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZtBr9z9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZtBr9z9.jpg&h=cb30d97e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2017 已經上過news<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2007/09/21/HK0709210019.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2007%2F09%2F21%2FHK0709210019.htm&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfLc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=d2fe80aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2007/09/21/HK0709210019.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 專呃導師錢<br />\n<br />\n中介費抽佣50%, 收錢介紹有問題補習之後賴死唔退錢<br />\n<br />\n2. 傾唔掂佢啲規矩, 俾佢問候又電話騷擾<br />\n<br />\n2007年俾黃大仙警署拉過, 涉嫌刑事恐嚇及詐騙家長同導師, 上埋庭見埋報 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 奇怪規矩<br />\n<br />\n需要佢陪同先可以上學生屋企補習, 唔俾導師家長電話聯絡, 過份收集導師資料<br />\n<br />\n希望大家小心d"},{"pid":"6491764d1da757920c39